{"tid":1472484,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日起只有同路人","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:54:27.000Z","uid":10367,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f43df1530e72638950b43e48ab721231310ab930","tid":1472484,"uid":10367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"今日開始只有同路人，唔再分咩勇武和理非，只有同一條路上互相扶持既手足。只係同一條路上大家代步工具唔同，有人選擇行路，有人選擇單車，但終究大家都係一齊行向終點。 <br />\n<br />\n果啲咩鬼啊，卧底啊就當過路人，只要大方向唔影響，理得佢電單車定單車，當佢係路過就得。<br />\n<br />\n為左犧牲左既同伴，為左被捕既同路人，係鬼節依一日，大家忘記啲鬼，重新團結啦好嗎？"},{"pid":"925a76a72d8f7d92cb95292383c600b69a1ec2c4","tid":1472484,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbQ9kzs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbQ9kzs.jpg&h=cc0ed30c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRczwF7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRczwF7.jpg&h=df32aafb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}